## 5. Animation & Transitions

### Required Transitions

| Element type                | Required transition                               |
| --------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Buttons (hover)             | `transition-colors`                               |
| Cards (hover/select)        | `transition-colors`                               |
| Accordion/collapsible       | `animate-accordion-down` / `animate-accordion-up` |
| Dropdown/popover appearance | Handled by Radix UI                               |
| Page transitions            | `transition-transform` if applicable              |

### Animation Tokens

| Token             | Value                              | Usage                        |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `--duration-550`  | 550ms                              | Standard transition duration |
| `--ease-out-expo` | `cubic-bezier(0.46, 0.7, 0.41, 1)` | Smooth deceleration          |

### Motion Sensitivity

- Always include `motion-safe:` or check `prefers-reduced-motion` for non-essential animations
- Loading spinners and skeletons are exempt (they serve a functional purpose)
- Decorative animations must be skippable

### FORBIDDEN Animation Patterns

- Animations longer than 1 second (feels sluggish)
- Animations that block user interaction
- Bounce or elastic easing on UI elements (feels unserious for a B2B product)
- Missing transitions on hover states (feels janky)

